{"node_id": "94d682ea0d25577c91cb816904f814ca", "title": "Derivatives of 𝑒ˣ and ln(x)", "description": "Use your knowledge of the derivatives of 𝑒ˣ and ln(x) to solve problems.", "topic_path": ["Khan Academy (English - US curriculum)", "Math", "AP®︎ Calculus AB", "Differentiation: definition and basic derivative rules", "Derivatives of cos(x), sin(x), 𝑒ˣ, and ln(x)", "Derivatives of 𝑒ˣ and ln(x)"], "assessment_items": [{"item_id": "bdfb3ea39410562da1e6b97bd3c3e5b3", "question_content": "Let $f(x)=2e^x-5\\text{cos}(x)+3$.\n\n$f'(x)=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$ and $\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{cos}(x)]=-\\text{sin}(x)}$.", "$\\begin{align}\nf'(x)&=\\dfrac{d}{dx}[2e^x-5\\text{cos}(x)+3]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=2\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}-5\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{cos}(x)]}+\\dfrac{d}{dx}[3]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=2\\cdot \\blueD{e^x}-5[\\maroonD{-\\text{sin}(x)}]+0\n\\\\\\\\\n&=2e^x+5\\text{sin}(x)\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$f'(x)=2e^x+5\\text{sin}(x)$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["2e^x+5\\sin(x)"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "2e^x+5\\sin(x)"}]}}}, {"item_id": "dbe8f402db7d54a194e89d2d030445b4", "question_content": "Let $g(x)=6\\text{sin}(x)-8e^x$.\n\n$g'(x)=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$ and $\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{sin}(x)]=\\text{cos}(x)}$.", "$\\begin{align}\ng'(x)&=\\dfrac{d}{dx}[6\\text{sin}(x)-8e^x]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=6\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{sin}(x)]}-8\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=6\\cdot\\maroonD{\\text{cos}(x)}-8\\blueD{e^x}\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$g'(x)=6\\text{cos}(x)-8e^x$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["6\\cos(x)-8e^x"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "6\\cos(x)-8e^x"}]}}}, {"item_id": "f892e5fc50aa579f852cd361aa11210c", "question_content": "Let $h(x)=x^3+7e^x$.\n\n$h'(x)=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$ and $\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[x^n]=nx^{n-1}}$.", "$\\begin{align}\nh'(x)&=\\dfrac{d}{dx}[x^3+7e^x]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[x^3]}+7\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=\\maroonD{3x^2}+7\\blueD{e^x}\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$h'(x)=3x^2+7e^x$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["3x^2+7e^x"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "3x^2+7e^x"}]}}}, {"item_id": "4cbced1b51845bcb8806d6e8b34d411b", "question_content": "Let $f(x)=-19e^x$.\n\n$f'(x)=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$.", "$\\begin{align}\nh'(x)&=\\dfrac{d}{dx}[-19e^x]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=-19\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=-19\\blueD{e^x}\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$f'(x)=-19e^x$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-19e^x"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "-19e^x"}]}}}, {"item_id": "4b95ae575e83581e89214442bb0a7a8f", "question_content": "$\\dfrac{d}{dx}[7\\text{cos}(x)+3e^x]=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$ and $\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{cos}(x)]=-\\text{sin}(x)}$.", "$\\begin{align}\n&\\phantom{=}\\dfrac{d}{dx}[7\\text{cos}(x)+3e^x]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=7\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{cos}(x)]}+3\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=7[\\maroonD{-\\text{sin}(x)}]+3\\blueD{e^x}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=-7\\text{sin}(x)+3e^x\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$\\dfrac{d}{dx}[7\\text{cos}(x)+3e^x]=-7\\text{sin}(x)+3e^x$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-7\\sin(x)+3e^x"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "-7\\sin(x)+3e^x"}]}}}, {"item_id": "67f64f5efebe5f33b5f0235d9db768df", "question_content": "$\\dfrac{d}{dx}[-4e^x-\\text{sin}(x)-9]=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$ and $\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{sin}(x)]=\\text{cos}(x)}$.", "$\\begin{align}\n&\\phantom{=}\\dfrac{d}{dx}[-4e^x-\\text{sin}(x)-9]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=-4\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}-\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{sin}(x)]}-\\dfrac{d}{dx}[9]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=-4\\blueD{e^x}-\\maroonD{\\text{cos}(x)}-0\n\\\\\\\\\n&=-4e^x-\\text{cos}(x)\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$\\dfrac{d}{dx}[-4e^x-\\text{sin}(x)-9]=-4e^x-\\text{cos}(x)$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-4e^x-\\cos(x)"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "-4e^x-\\cos(x)"}]}}}, {"item_id": "be5c73921e9d5e02a8307e2780792e01", "question_content": "$\\dfrac{d}{dx}[3e^x+5x^2]=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]=e^x}$ and $\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[x^n]=nx^{n-1}}$.", "$\\begin{align}\n&\\phantom{=}\\dfrac{d}{dx}[3e^x+5x^2]\n\\\\\\\\\n&=3\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[e^x]}+5\\maroonD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[x^2]}\n\\\\\\\\\n&=3\\cdot\\blueD{e^x}+5(\\maroonD{2x^1})\n\\\\\\\\\n&=3e^x+10x\n\\end{align}$", "In conclusion,\n\n$\\dfrac{d}{dx}[3e^x+5x^2]=3e^x+10x$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["3e^x+10x"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": false, "value": "3e^x+10x"}]}}}, {"item_id": "568040a1bb665e10800cad3a1c7a1f72", "question_content": "Let $f(x)=-4\\text{sin}(x)-9\\text{ln}(x)+11$.\n\n$f'(x)=$ [[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Recall that $\\blueD{\\dfrac{d}{dx}[\\text{ln}(x)]=\\dfrac1x}$ and $\\maroonD